1956;;A Woman's Devotion;;American;;Paul Henreid;;Janice Rule, Ralph Meeker;;film noir;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/A_Woman%27s_Devotion;;Artist Trevor Stevenson (Meeker), an emotionally scarred World War II veteran, is on honeymoon in Acapulco with his bride Stella (Rule). Shortly after their arrival, two women are murdered. The audience is presented with clues pointing to Trevor's guilt or innocence depending upon one's point of view.